    "name": "Mesh Independence Study for CPB CFD Model",
    "description": "A systematic mesh refinement study was conducted across three mesh densities (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 5.8M cells, fine: 14.3M cells) to assess discretization error in the hemolysis scalar transport equation. The Grid Convergence Index (GCI) methodology per ASME V&V 20 was applied to quantify numerical uncertainty in the predicted relative hemolysis index at each of the five operating points.",
    "activityType": "MeshRefinementStudy",
