    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all five evaluated operating points, and validation comparisons are within the 15% acceptance band. The credibility assessment supports regulatory submission.",
